    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="icon" href="../assets/favicons/central-ministry.svg" />
    <title>Central Ministry</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    
    <section class="content">
      <div class="central-ministry logo-frame">
        <div class="central-ministry logo-lottie">
          <!-- logo animation goes here -->
        </div>
      </div>
      <section class="hero">
        <h1 class="hero-title">We make the big decisions in Government.</h1>
        <p class="hero-text">
          The Central Ministry is the leading authority of the Government, responsible for major
          announcements and having the final say in Government decisions.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section class="ministers">
        <h2 class="ministers heading">Ministers</h2>
        <div class="section-divider"></div>
        <div class="ministers list">
          <div class="minister">
            <div class="minister picture" id="pbb"></div>
            <div class="minister info-box">
              <h4 class="minister name">Pink Bear Bear</h4>
              <h5 class="minister job-title">Prime Minister</h5>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="minister">
            <div class="minister picture" id="apb"></div>
            <div class="minister info-box">
              <h4 class="minister name">Another Pink Bear</h4>
              <h5 class="minister job-title">Deputy Prime Minister</h5>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="tasks">
        <h2 class="tasks heading">What we do</h2>
        <div class="section-divider"></div>
        <h3 class="tasks title">Oversee Government</h3>
        <p class="tasks text">
          We work with all other Government ministries to plan, coordinate and execute new policies.
          As the leading authority of the Government, we ensure the Government works efficiently and
          effectively to enable plushies to live life to the fullest.
        </p>
        <h3 class="tasks title">Inform citizens</h3>
        <p class="tasks text">
          We are responsible for delivering important announcements on major developments in the
          Government and the Kingdom. These announcements are available here in the
          <a class="link" href="/news/">Government news page</a>, as well as on our
          <a
            class="link"
            href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCL4Px1LLyD6WxcaDTm71ViQ"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
            >YouTube channel</a
          >.
        </p>
        <h3 class="tasks title">Maintain the Government identity</h3>
        <p class="tasks text">
          We ensure that Government information and services remain consistent across all platforms
          by ensuring all of it closely follows our
          <a class="link" href="/about/gov-identity/">identity guidelines</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </section>
    <a class="return" href="/">Return to homepage</a>
